long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
PhabTab makes it easy to keep track of your Phabricator reviews right from the Chrome toolbar.

Features include:
 - lists reviews waiting on your review
 - lists reviews you've authored that are ready to land
 - separates reviews you've responded to but not yet accepted from reviews you haven't responded to since the author last made a change
 - displays a count of reviews waiting for your attention directly as a badge in the toolbar
 - supports reviews assigned to you directly and reviews assigned to groups to which you belong

PhabTab requires minimal permissions and is open source under the Apache 2 license.

Phabricator is a trademark of Phacility, Inc. PhabTab has no relation to Phacility, Inc.

Icons based on review by Bombasticon Studio from the Noun Project.
